{{spoiler}} {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Moebius |image = Moebius_Boss.jpg |caption = Moebius |category = Boss |type = [[Moebius]] |level = 10 |area = [[Alfeto Valley]] ([[Gura Flava Lowlands]]) |spawntime = Story |respawn = No |movement = Ground |exp = 448 |cp = 55 |hp = 20,650 |sp = 0 |gold = 0 |strength = 83 |healing = 82 |dexterity = 47 |agility = 30 |physdef = 0% |ethdef = 15% |critrate = 0% |guardrate = 0% }} The '''Moebius''' is a [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] in {{XC3}}. It is fought at level 10 in the [[Gura Flava Lowlands]] in [[Alfeto Valley]] after being fought as [[Mysterious Enemy]]. Both enemies share near-identical data, the only differences being the lower HP of the Moebius fight as well as differences in AI Arts usage. During this battle, [[Noah]] will be able to use his [[Ouroboros]] at [[Interlink]] Level 0 for an unlimited amount of time. It is later fought and revealed as being [[Moebius D & J]].
